name: The Money Nerds Podcast
what_you_do: The Money Nerds Podcast provides financial coaching and advice, focusing on helping high-income healthcare professionals manage their finances, crush student loans, and achieve semi-retirement.
who_you_serve: The podcast primarily serves high-income healthcare professionals, including physician assistants and nurse practitioners, who are looking to improve their financial literacy and wealth-building strategies.
bio: Wilson Liang is a physician assistant, professor, and financial coach, recognized for his expertise in helping others achieve financial independence.
